fix(display-tablets): correct parameter validation schemas

Fixed validation schemas for GET and POST endpoints that were incorrectly
expecting both householdId and tabletId parameters when they should only
expect householdId.

- GET /v1/households/:householdId/display-tablets now uses householdParamsSchema
- POST /v1/households/:householdId/display-tablets now uses householdParamsSchema
- Other endpoints correctly use householdTabletParamsSchema when both IDs needed
